  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Coronavirus (COVID-19): jobs that qualify for travel exemptions
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Jobs that qualify for exemptions from self-isolation or passenger locator form requirements.</p>

  </div>
</div>

